snippet.textDisplay:
Just can't believe my eyes seeing them both (Noman & Babar Bhai) in a world renowned international platform like Coke Studio and listening them both singing song in their and my mother tongue Sindhi.  ❤

I've witnessed their journey from beginning to this moment. I am literally overwhelmed seeing my language being promoted to the whole world in such melodious voices like them. 

Wholeheartedly thankful to the whole team of Coke Studio for making this long awaited dream of every Sindhi a reality. 🙏❤

Looking forward to see more Sindhi gems promoting Sindhi culture and music in the upcoming episodes and seasons. 😍
